ân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-Tr%E1%BB%9F-phong-s%C6%A1n-phong-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-Od60uMxmye0bf3lJZIYwvQ">Tây giang nguyệt - Trở phong sơn phong hạ - 西江月－阻風山峰下</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-77k7d_i26Q3zI_gu_1iz-w">Trương Hiếu Tường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-d%C3%A3-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-gyhBQayHiESs4CloF5lMdQ">Thu dã kỳ 4 - 秋野其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91-trung-t%C3%ACnh-T%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-Hg-7eOvtAxpY8-66f5D-4Q">Tố trung tình - Tụng điếu giả - 訴衷情－頌釣者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BA%A5u/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-rql-jZnNbaNuIEUGa7BJKA">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BA%A5u/author-5qWci72__CfS8kAB5nVXFA">Vương Cấu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
